Description: Trainddata files for specific languages
DescPackaging: <<
	We follow Debian's lead, placing files in the 5/tessdata/script/
	subdir and in a separate package for each language.
<<
DescUsage: <<
	Install a specific tesseract-lang-XXX language of interest,
	or tesseract-lang-all as the whole collection.
<<
